data.title: Sound of Lightbulbs for Omnisphere
data.meta_description: Lumos is soundset for Spectrasonics Omnisphere based on the psychoacoustic sounds of lightbulbs.

FORMAT: OMNISPHERE

STYLE: AMBIENT / EXPERIMENTAL / LAMPS

Lumos is an ambient orchestra of sounds based on nothing else but the sounds of lamps. From cozy 40 watt lightbulbs all the way up to illuminating 200 watt.

"let there be light! lumos is an ambient collection of sounds based on the sounds of... lamps!"
